{
  "stem": "748.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she give it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This cost-- used to cost a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she give it to my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't cry, Esther, she says, I have mine child's birth certificate, and I will take the child and I will give care of him.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the child was with the-- my mother's friend, an older woman, a very nice person.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she lives on the-- on the same street with my mother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- Do you remember what the-- the-- the street name was?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the boy was with-- he called this lady grandmother, bapchu.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once, shortly before the German-- the Germans went-- the Russians came into Lublin, this child was-- she let him more be freely in-- in the street to play with kids.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, went a Polish policeman-- his name is Dulski.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] He was-- yeah, he was a policeman, but he never weared police clothes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just with the SS men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went through.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And mine son played-- this is what the lady told me later, because I ran away after the war was finished.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went to Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I says, this child must be alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, when I came-- and the Polish policeman says to the SS man, this is Jude-- of the-- of the-- the boy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He knew, because he lived not far away from [? us. ?] The-- that German took the revolver and shot him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes. 10 days before the Russians came in to Lublin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then, when the war was end, because I was a witness in Leninburg, was a protest from the SS man.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
